{"slug":"os","title":"并发控制与信号量全景复习指南","date":"2026-06-18","category":"OS","tags":["OS","learning"],"excerpt":"并发控制与信号量全景复习指南","minutes":5,"wordCount":1444,"accent":"teal","body":"<h2 id=\"第一阶段基础控制流--纯同步与顺序铁律\">第一阶段：基础控制流 —— 纯同步与“顺序铁律”</h2>\r\n<p><strong>核心目标：</strong> 理解资源信号量与互斥锁的嵌套规则，避免最基础的死锁。</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"1-场景带入多生产者-多消费者问题\">1. 场景带入：多生产者-多消费者问题</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>独特性：</strong> 系统中有两类角色（生产者、消费者），操作<strong>同一个</strong>资源池（比如长度为 N 的缓冲区）。这里没有“同类并发”，任何人操作缓冲区都必须绝对互斥。</li>\r\n<li><strong>业务痛点：</strong> 消费者去取数据时，如果缓冲区为空，必须挂起等待；生产者去放数据时，如果缓冲区满了，也必须挂起等待。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"2-深入分析p操作的顺序铁律\">2. 深入分析：P操作的“顺序铁律”</h3>\r\n<p>如果我们先加互斥锁，再申请资源，就会触发“带锁睡眠”（请求与保持）：消费者锁住了缓冲区，发现没数据，带着锁睡着了；生产者想发数据，却拿不到缓冲区的锁，导致死局。</p>\r\n<p>因此，<strong>必须先进行资源 P 操作（排队等资源），再进行互斥 P 操作（拿钥匙开门）。</strong></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"3-伪代码实现\">3. 伪代码实现</h3>\r\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb1\"><pre class=\"sourceCode c\"><code class=\"sourceCode c\"><span id=\"cb1-1\"><a href=\"#cb1-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore empty <span class=\"op\">=</span> N<span class=\"op\">;</span>    <span class=\"co\">// 空闲槽位，初始为 N</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-2\"><a href=\"#cb1-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore full <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>     <span class=\"co\">// 已有数据，初始为 0</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-3\"><a href=\"#cb1-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore mutex <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>    <span class=\"co\">// 缓冲区互斥锁</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-4\"><a href=\"#cb1-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-5\"><a href=\"#cb1-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>Process Producer<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-6\"><a href=\"#cb1-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">while</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span><span class=\"kw\">true</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-7\"><a href=\"#cb1-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        生产数据 item<span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-8\"><a href=\"#cb1-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        P<span class=\"op\">(</span>empty<span class=\"op\">);</span>       <span class=\"co\">// 【铁律】先等空位，没有空位就在门外干净地睡去</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-9\"><a href=\"#cb1-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        P<span class=\"op\">(</span>mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>       <span class=\"co\">// 拿到空位了，再锁缓冲区大门</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-10\"><a href=\"#cb1-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        将 item 放入缓冲区<span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-11\"><a href=\"#cb1-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        V<span class=\"op\">(</span>mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>       <span class=\"co\">// 解锁大门</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-12\"><a href=\"#cb1-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        V<span class=\"op\">(</span>full<span class=\"op\">);</span>        <span class=\"co\">// 通知消费者：有新数据了！</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-13\"><a href=\"#cb1-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-14\"><a href=\"#cb1-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-15\"><a href=\"#cb1-15\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-16\"><a href=\"#cb1-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>Process Consumer<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-17\"><a href=\"#cb1-17\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">while</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span><span class=\"kw\">true</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-18\"><a href=\"#cb1-18\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        P<span class=\"op\">(</span>full<span class=\"op\">);</span>        <span class=\"co\">// 【铁律】先等数据</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-19\"><a href=\"#cb1-19\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        P<span class=\"op\">(</span>mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>       <span class=\"co\">// 再锁大门</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-20\"><a href=\"#cb1-20\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        从缓冲区取出 item<span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-21\"><a href=\"#cb1-21\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        V<span class=\"op\">(</span>mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-22\"><a href=\"#cb1-22\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        V<span class=\"op\">(</span>empty<span class=\"op\">);</span>       <span class=\"co\">// 通知生产者：腾出空位了！</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-23\"><a href=\"#cb1-23\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb1-24\"><a href=\"#cb1-24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"link-递进思考通往第二阶段\">🔗 递进思考（通往第二阶段）：</h3>\r\n<p>第一阶段的模型是“绝对互斥”的，一次只能进一个人。但在实际业务中（如数据库查询），如果大家都是“只读不写”，为什么不能一起进去看呢？这就引出了同类并发的需求。</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"第二阶段状态接力--经典读者优先模型\">第二阶段：状态接力 —— 经典读者优先模型</h2>\r\n<p><strong>核心目标：</strong> 实现“同类并发，异类互斥”，理解第一个和最后一个角色的特殊使命。</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"1-场景带入经典读者-写者问题读者优先\">1. 场景带入：经典读者-写者问题（读者优先）</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>独特性：</strong> 区分了操作类型。读者与读者可以共享资源（同类并发），写者与任何人互斥（异类互斥）。</li>\r\n<li><strong>业务痛点：</strong> 读者不能每次都去抢最高级别的读写锁，否则并发度退化为 1。我们需要一种机制，让第一个读者负责“锁死写者”，后续的读者直接“乘凉”。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"2-深入分析最后离开的人负责关灯\">2. 深入分析：“最后离开的人负责关灯”</h3>\r\n<p>引入一个共享计数器 <code>rc</code>。</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>第 1 个读者：发现 <code>rc == 1</code>，负责执行 <code>P(wmutex)</code> 拦住写者。</li>\r\n<li>第 2~N 个读者：发现 <code>rc &gt; 1</code>，直接进去读，无视写者。</li>\r\n<li>最后 1 个读者：发现 <code>rc == 0</code>，负责执行 <code>V(wmutex)</code> 放写者进来。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"3-伪代码实现-1\">3. 伪代码实现</h3>\r\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb2\"><pre class=\"sourceCode c\"><code class=\"sourceCode c\"><span id=\"cb2-1\"><a href=\"#cb2-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dt\">int</span> rc <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>             <span class=\"co\">// 读者数量</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-2\"><a href=\"#cb2-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore rmutex <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>   <span class=\"co\">// 保护 rc 的修改</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-3\"><a href=\"#cb2-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore wmutex <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>   <span class=\"co\">// 读写互斥、写写互斥大锁</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-4\"><a href=\"#cb2-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-5\"><a href=\"#cb2-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>Process Reader<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-6\"><a href=\"#cb2-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">while</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span><span class=\"kw\">true</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-7\"><a href=\"#cb2-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        P<span class=\"op\">(</span>rmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-8\"><a href=\"#cb2-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        rc<span class=\"op\">++;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-9\"><a href=\"#cb2-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>rc <span class=\"op\">==</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> P<span class=\"op\">(</span>wmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span> <span class=\"co\">// 第一个读者，负责锁死写者</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-10\"><a href=\"#cb2-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        V<span class=\"op\">(</span>rmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-11\"><a href=\"#cb2-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-12\"><a href=\"#cb2-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        执行读操作<span class=\"op\">...</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>此处高并发<span class=\"op\">)</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-13\"><a href=\"#cb2-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-14\"><a href=\"#cb2-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        P<span class=\"op\">(</span>rmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-15\"><a href=\"#cb2-15\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        rc<span class=\"op\">--;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-16\"><a href=\"#cb2-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>rc <span class=\"op\">==</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> V<span class=\"op\">(</span>wmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span> <span class=\"co\">// 最后一个读者，负责唤醒写者</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-17\"><a href=\"#cb2-17\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        V<span class=\"op\">(</span>rmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-18\"><a href=\"#cb2-18\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-19\"><a href=\"#cb2-19\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-20\"><a href=\"#cb2-20\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-21\"><a href=\"#cb2-21\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>Process Writer<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-22\"><a href=\"#cb2-22\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">while</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span><span class=\"kw\">true</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-23\"><a href=\"#cb2-23\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        P<span class=\"op\">(</span>wmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>      <span class=\"co\">// 写者极其卑微，只要有读者在里面，就拿不到锁</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-24\"><a href=\"#cb2-24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        执行写操作<span class=\"op\">...</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-25\"><a href=\"#cb2-25\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        V<span class=\"op\">(</span>wmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-26\"><a href=\"#cb2-26\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb2-27\"><a href=\"#cb2-27\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"link-递进思考通往第三阶段\">🔗 递进思考（通往第三阶段）：</h3>\r\n<p>读者优先模型极其<strong>不公平</strong>。只要读者源源不断（<code>rc</code> 永远降不到 0），写者就会被无情地<strong>饿死（Starvation）</strong>。如何保障写者的基本人权，实现“先来先服务”？</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"第三阶段空间解耦--旋转闸机模式公平读写\">第三阶段：空间解耦 —— 旋转闸机模式（公平读写）</h2>\r\n<p><strong>核心目标：</strong> 剥离“排队权”与“执行权”，强行截断读者的无脑连击。</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"1-场景带入读写公平问题如余票并发查询与购买\">1. 场景带入：读写公平问题（如：余票并发查询与购买）</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>独特性：</strong> 既要保留“读者并发”，又要保证“写者不饿死”。即：如果写者开始排队了，后面的读者必须停下来等写者写完。</li>\r\n<li><strong>业务痛点：</strong> 必须有一个极轻量级的锁，让大家先来“取号”。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"2-深入分析单向卡脖子法则\">2. 深入分析：单向卡脖子法则</h3>\r\n<p>引入 <code>queue_mutex</code>（闸机）。</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>读者进闸机，拿号登记后，<strong>立刻出闸机</strong>。</li>\r\n<li>写者进闸机，如果发现里面有读者，他会<strong>带着闸机锁死死睡去（物理堵门）</strong>！他这一堵，后面的读者全被截断，只能等写者写完。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"3-伪代码实现-2\">3. 伪代码实现</h3>\r\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb3\"><pre class=\"sourceCode c\"><code class=\"sourceCode c\"><span id=\"cb3-1\"><a href=\"#cb3-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore queue_mutex <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span> <span class=\"co\">// 公平闸机锁</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-2\"><a href=\"#cb3-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore rw_mutex <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>    <span class=\"co\">// 读写互斥锁</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-3\"><a href=\"#cb3-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore rmutex <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>      <span class=\"co\">// 保护 rc</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-4\"><a href=\"#cb3-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dt\">int</span> rc <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-5\"><a href=\"#cb3-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-6\"><a href=\"#cb3-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>Process Reader<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-7\"><a href=\"#cb3-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>queue_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>      <span class=\"co\">// 1. 进闸机排队</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-8\"><a href=\"#cb3-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>rmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-9\"><a href=\"#cb3-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    rc<span class=\"op\">++;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-10\"><a href=\"#cb3-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>rc <span class=\"op\">==</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> P<span class=\"op\">(</span>rw_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span> </span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-11\"><a href=\"#cb3-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>rmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-12\"><a href=\"#cb3-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>queue_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>      <span class=\"co\">// 2. 读者秒退闸机，放下一位进场</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-13\"><a href=\"#cb3-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-14\"><a href=\"#cb3-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    查询操作<span class=\"op\">...</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-15\"><a href=\"#cb3-15\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-16\"><a href=\"#cb3-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>rmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-17\"><a href=\"#cb3-17\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    rc<span class=\"op\">--;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-18\"><a href=\"#cb3-18\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>rc <span class=\"op\">==</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> V<span class=\"op\">(</span>rw_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span> <span class=\"co\">// 里面没人了，放写者进业务区</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-19\"><a href=\"#cb3-19\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>rmutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-20\"><a href=\"#cb3-20\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-21\"><a href=\"#cb3-21\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-22\"><a href=\"#cb3-22\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>Process Writer<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-23\"><a href=\"#cb3-23\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>queue_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>      <span class=\"co\">// 1. 写者进闸机</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-24\"><a href=\"#cb3-24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>rw_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>         <span class=\"co\">// 2. 尝试进业务区。如果不成功，带着 queue_mutex 睡眠！强行截断后面排队的读者！</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-25\"><a href=\"#cb3-25\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>queue_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>      <span class=\"co\">// 3. 醒来后，放行后面的队伍</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-26\"><a href=\"#cb3-26\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-27\"><a href=\"#cb3-27\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    购买操作<span class=\"op\">...</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-28\"><a href=\"#cb3-28\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-29\"><a href=\"#cb3-29\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>rw_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span>         <span class=\"co\">// 写完离开</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb3-30\"><a href=\"#cb3-30\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"link-递进思考通往第四阶段\">🔗 递进思考（通往第四阶段）：</h3>\r\n<p>这里的写者是“绝对独占”的（一次只能写一个）。如果现在的场景变了，有两个阵营，<strong>两个阵营内部都能并发，但两个阵营之间互斥</strong>，该怎么利用“带锁睡眠”？</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"第四阶段镜像双雄--对称的候诊室-手术室模型\">第四阶段：镜像双雄 —— 对称的“候诊室-手术室”模型</h2>\r\n<p><strong>核心目标：</strong> 解决复杂的同性并发、异性互斥、且绝对公平的问题。</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"1-场景带入单行道木桥问题或男女浴室问题\">1. 场景带入：单行道木桥问题（或男女浴室问题）</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>独特性：</strong> 这是一个“双写者（双读者）”模型。东向车和西向车都是“读者”（可以同向并发），但彼此互为“写者”（逆向绝对互斥）。</li>\r\n<li><strong>业务痛点：</strong> 需要对称的双重计数器，并且需要一个统一的收费站（闸机）来维持绝对公平。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"2-深入分析对称拦截与状态接力\">2. 深入分析：对称拦截与状态接力</h3>\r\n<p>将闸机模式完全镜像化。</p>\r\n<p>桥面上全是东向车时，西向车进闸机，发现桥面被占，就会在收费站（闸机）里<strong>带锁睡眠</strong>，堵死后续所有的东向车。等最后一辆东向车下桥，西向车苏醒，瞬间反锁桥面，开启西向的高并发时代。</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"3-伪代码实现-3\">3. 伪代码实现</h3>\r\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb4\"><pre class=\"sourceCode c\"><code class=\"sourceCode c\"><span id=\"cb4-1\"><a href=\"#cb4-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore turnstile <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>  <span class=\"co\">// 桥头收费站（闸机）</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-2\"><a href=\"#cb4-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore bridge <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span>     <span class=\"co\">// 桥面使用权</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-3\"><a href=\"#cb4-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dt\">int</span> east_cnt <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">,</span> west_cnt <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-4\"><a href=\"#cb4-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>semaphore east_mutex <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">,</span> west_mutex <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-5\"><a href=\"#cb4-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-6\"><a href=\"#cb4-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>Process EastBound<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span> <span class=\"co\">// 向东的车</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-7\"><a href=\"#cb4-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>turnstile<span class=\"op\">);</span>         <span class=\"co\">// 进收费站</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-8\"><a href=\"#cb4-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    </span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-9\"><a href=\"#cb4-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>east_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-10\"><a href=\"#cb4-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    east_cnt<span class=\"op\">++;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-11\"><a href=\"#cb4-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>east_cnt <span class=\"op\">==</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> P<span class=\"op\">(</span>bridge<span class=\"op\">);</span> <span class=\"co\">// 第一辆东向车，锁死桥面</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-12\"><a href=\"#cb4-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>east_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-13\"><a href=\"#cb4-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    </span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-14\"><a href=\"#cb4-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>turnstile<span class=\"op\">);</span>         <span class=\"co\">// 【精髓】立刻交出收费站，允许同向车跟上，或让逆向车进来堵门</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-15\"><a href=\"#cb4-15\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-16\"><a href=\"#cb4-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    向东过桥<span class=\"op\">...</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>高并发行驶<span class=\"op\">)</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-17\"><a href=\"#cb4-17\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-18\"><a href=\"#cb4-18\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>east_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-19\"><a href=\"#cb4-19\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    east_cnt<span class=\"op\">--;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-20\"><a href=\"#cb4-20\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>east_cnt <span class=\"op\">==</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> V<span class=\"op\">(</span>bridge<span class=\"op\">);</span> <span class=\"co\">// 最后一辆下桥，解开桥面，唤醒死等在收费站的西向车</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-21\"><a href=\"#cb4-21\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>east_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-22\"><a href=\"#cb4-22\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-23\"><a href=\"#cb4-23\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-24\"><a href=\"#cb4-24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>Process WestBound<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span> <span class=\"co\">// 向西的车（逻辑完全对称）</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-25\"><a href=\"#cb4-25\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>turnstile<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-26\"><a href=\"#cb4-26\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    </span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-27\"><a href=\"#cb4-27\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>west_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-28\"><a href=\"#cb4-28\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    west_cnt<span class=\"op\">++;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-29\"><a href=\"#cb4-29\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>west_cnt <span class=\"op\">==</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> P<span class=\"op\">(</span>bridge<span class=\"op\">);</span> <span class=\"co\">// 如果桥上是东向车，这辆西向车就会带锁死睡，截断东向车流</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-30\"><a href=\"#cb4-30\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>west_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-31\"><a href=\"#cb4-31\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    </span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-32\"><a href=\"#cb4-32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>turnstile<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-33\"><a href=\"#cb4-33\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-34\"><a href=\"#cb4-34\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    向西过桥<span class=\"op\">...</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-35\"><a href=\"#cb4-35\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-36\"><a href=\"#cb4-36\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    P<span class=\"op\">(</span>west_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-37\"><a href=\"#cb4-37\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    west_cnt<span class=\"op\">--;</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-38\"><a href=\"#cb4-38\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(</span>west_cnt <span class=\"op\">==</span> <span class=\"dv\">0</span><span class=\"op\">)</span> V<span class=\"op\">(</span>bridge<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-39\"><a href=\"#cb4-39\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    V<span class=\"op\">(</span>west_mutex<span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\r\n<span id=\"cb4-40\"><a href=\"#cb4-40\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n<h2 id=\"checkered_flag-终极归纳法则你的架构心法\">🏁 终极归纳法则（你的架构心法）</h2>\r\n<p>当你以后在试卷或工程中，看到任何复杂的同步描述时，请直接进行如下思想映射：</p>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li><strong>只要涉及“具体条件失败时要回退（如没钱不买）”：</strong> 抛弃纯信号量，使用 <code>Mutex + int变量</code>，主动 Fail-fast 退出。</li>\r\n<li><strong>只要涉及“同类可以一起操作”：</strong> 必须引入 <code>count</code> 变量和首尾接力判断（第一个拿锁，最后一个放锁）。</li>\r\n<li><strong>只要涉及“防止饿死 / 按顺序排队”：</strong> 必须在最外层套一层极轻量级的 <code>Turnstile</code> 闸机锁。只包裹“取号”过程，绝不包裹业务全过程。</li>\r\n<li><strong>只要涉及“强行打断对方的高并发”：</strong> 勇敢地利用“物理堵门”，让弱势的一方在闸机里执行 <code>P(业务大门)</code>，实现<strong>安全的带锁睡眠</strong>（前提是：对方出来时不需要碰闸机锁）。</li>\r\n</ol>","headings":[{"depth":2,"id":"第一阶段基础控制流--纯同步与顺序铁律","text":"第一阶段：基础控制流 —— 纯同步与“顺序铁律”"},{"depth":3,"id":"1-场景带入多生产者-多消费者问题","text":"1. 场景带入：多生产者-多消费者问题"},{"depth":3,"id":"2-深入分析p操作的顺序铁律","text":"2. 深入分析：P操作的“顺序铁律”"},{"depth":3,"id":"3-伪代码实现","text":"3. 伪代码实现"},{"depth":3,"id":"link-递进思考通往第二阶段","text":"🔗 递进思考（通往第二阶段）："},{"depth":2,"id":"第二阶段状态接力--经典读者优先模型","text":"第二阶段：状态接力 —— 经典读者优先模型"},{"depth":3,"id":"1-场景带入经典读者-写者问题读者优先","text":"1. 场景带入：经典读者-写者问题（读者优先）"},{"depth":3,"id":"2-深入分析最后离开的人负责关灯","text":"2. 深入分析：“最后离开的人负责关灯”"},{"depth":3,"id":"3-伪代码实现-1","text":"3. 伪代码实现"},{"depth":3,"id":"link-递进思考通往第三阶段","text":"🔗 递进思考（通往第三阶段）："},{"depth":2,"id":"第三阶段空间解耦--旋转闸机模式公平读写","text":"第三阶段：空间解耦 —— 旋转闸机模式（公平读写）"},{"depth":3,"id":"1-场景带入读写公平问题如余票并发查询与购买","text":"1. 场景带入：读写公平问题（如：余票并发查询与购买）"},{"depth":3,"id":"2-深入分析单向卡脖子法则","text":"2. 深入分析：单向卡脖子法则"},{"depth":3,"id":"3-伪代码实现-2","text":"3. 伪代码实现"},{"depth":3,"id":"link-递进思考通往第四阶段","text":"🔗 递进思考（通往第四阶段）："},{"depth":2,"id":"第四阶段镜像双雄--对称的候诊室-手术室模型","text":"第四阶段：镜像双雄 —— 对称的“候诊室-手术室”模型"},{"depth":3,"id":"1-场景带入单行道木桥问题或男女浴室问题","text":"1. 场景带入：单行道木桥问题（或男女浴室问题）"},{"depth":3,"id":"2-深入分析对称拦截与状态接力","text":"2. 深入分析：对称拦截与状态接力"},{"depth":3,"id":"3-伪代码实现-3","text":"3. 伪代码实现"},{"depth":2,"id":"checkered_flag-终极归纳法则你的架构心法","text":"🏁 终极归纳法则（你的架构心法）"}]}
